I got to reconnect with my friend, Dawnn Lewis. Did you know her story about how she got on A Different World? It starts with her writing the theme song that Aretha made famous. I get to chat with her and other cast mates tonight at Elizabeth City State University!  See you there
What a wonderful time I had at @ecsuvikings homecoming! The Viking Spirit is strong and they made me feel like I was a cast member from A Different World. Long Live Hillman College and all #hbcus

What can I say about this man? 
Today he takes a one way trip to Los Angeles and though I want to hold him close, it’s my job to let him go and soar. Khalil Gibran says “You are the bows from which your children as living arrows are sent forth.” 
So I load, pull back my bow…take aim. ~BREATH~
 I fire, knowing God made me a hot shot. His preparation was slow and skilled. 
So, my beautiful only son. 
You are prepared, favored and have been provided with all the skills and faith to receive the desires of your heart and more.  Jeremiah 29:11 For I know the plans I have for you, declares the Lord, plans to prosper you and not to harm you, plans to give you hope and a future”
Pop Pop says, You got a future! That’s confirmation.
I love you Little A! 
Mommy
